trans-unit.source: This property provides the ability to access a specific element in the collection by using the following syntax: `myCollection[index]`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult> elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult> elementos que siguen al agregado <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientResult> se desplazan hacia arriba para ocupar el espacio libre.
